All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Class
The record class represents a class in a schedule.
Controller
The Controller class is the controller of the application, it shows the schedule of a group using a grid.
Data
The Class Data is a singleton class that contains all the data of the problem.
Driver
The Driver class runs the evolutionary algorithm to generate a schedule.
Group
The record group represents a group of students that share the same subjects.
Individual
The Individual class stores the chromosome and fitness of an individual.
Main
The Main class is the entry point of the application.
Population
The Population class stores an array of individuals and their total fitness.
Room
The record room represents a room where a class takes place.
Schedule
The class Schedule stores the classes of a schedule.
Subject
The record subject represents a subject that is taught in a class.
Time
The record time represents a time slot where a class takes place.
